text: Jose Vicente Gimeno Sendra (3 July 1949 - 22 November 2020) was a Spanish politician and lawyer. He was born in Gandia, Spain. He was a Judge on the Constitutional Court of Spain from 1989 to 1998. Gimeno Sendra died on 22 November 2020 at the age of 71.Tenía 71 años: fallece Vicente Gimeno Sendra, exmagistrado del Constitucional y jurista muy reconocido ==References== Category:1949 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Spanish politicians Category:Spanish lawyers
